Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.13,0:00:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Atri...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.80,0:00:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,A warm room, delicious food,\Nfriends who cherished you...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.64,0:00:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You had all that just because you\Nwere born as royalty in this country...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.93,0:00:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that was ridiculous from\Nthe bottom of my heart, Prince Zen!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.52,0:00:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what you think of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.86,0:00:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still looking for answers...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.04,0:00:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Atri!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.08,0:00:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It might've been better...\Nif you hadn't been a prince...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.06,0:00:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We all, at any given time,\Ndesire real connections with others...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.40,0:01:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,On this path that we cannot stop walking on...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.44,0:01:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,For something to stir us up\Nfrom the depths of our hearts...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.74,0:01:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That is what we are looking for...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.08,0:02:56.67,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,"Episode 9: Feelings that Connect and Reach"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.21,0:02:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.50,0:02:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,How is Shirayuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.51,0:03:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,She's awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.84,0:03:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,She looks like she's still a little drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.97,0:03:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, she does.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.26,0:03:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be finishing up work in the office,\Nso sorry, but please look after her, Obi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.69,0:03:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.90,0:03:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you feeling, Miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.24,0:03:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.62,0:03:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.21,0:03:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me. Chief herbalist, is Obi here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.87,0:03:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,He wasn't in the room?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.71,0:03:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I had him look after Shirayuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.05,0:03:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Look after her? Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.30,0:03:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, no, just...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.84,0:03:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,She passed out after I had her\Ndrink some strong liquor as a joke...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.39,0:03:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirayuki really couldn't hold her liquor...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.02,0:03:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I'm having her rest until she sobers up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.77,0:03:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,In the room?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.73,0:03:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.61,0:04:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirayuki was not there, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.44,0:04:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.07,0:04:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead, I found a note to Zen...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.78,0:04:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm... well... was Obi with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.53,0:04:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.66,0:04:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Well if she's with someone authorized\Nby the prince, then it should be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.88,0:04:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Are you sure you're\Nall right walking around?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.30,0:04:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? That girl is down there right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.43,0:04:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.60,0:04:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, Prince Zen's fiancée...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.93,0:04:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.27,0:04:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So she's the one?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.90,0:04:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Her red hair is so unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.74,0:04:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's not like there's a need to hide...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.87,0:04:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Jackets, household medicines\Nthey were running out of...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.46,0:04:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No, wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.63,0:05:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't ride a horse...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.17,0:05:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,A horse?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.55,0:05:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. Mitsuhide\Nlet me ride with him before...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.97,0:05:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh, if I had an older brother,\NI think he'd be like Mitsuhide...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.56,0:05:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,--She sure is drunk...\N--Wait, what I need right now\Nis a horse... A horse...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.23,0:05:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,--A horse? Why a horse?\N--A horse... A horse...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.15,0:05:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss, are you thinking of\Ngoing to Tanbarun or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.03,0:05:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's Lord Haruka!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.57,0:05:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Why aren't you looking?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.12,0:05:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Like he'd be there so conveniently.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.33,0:05:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like I can take\Nmy eyes off you, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.54,0:05:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you guarding me today after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.88,0:05:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.30,0:05:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It would've been better\Nif the master did it, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.05,0:05:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What? It wouldn't have been better?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.18,0:05:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If I borrowed the prince for a day,\Nthen Lord Haruka really {\i1}would{\i0} be angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.02,0:06:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Oh, yeah, that's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.44,0:06:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.11,0:06:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.12,0:06:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, did he notice me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.37,0:06:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh well, I'll just finish today's report...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.46,0:06:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you wait here for a sec?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.00,0:06:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.17,0:06:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.52,0:06:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,"Red. There was contact.\NThe sun set with no wind blowing."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.06,0:06:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,"Red"... That's Shirayuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.52,0:06:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Does "there was contact"\Nmean she saw Prince Zen?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.57,0:06:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like you didn't see anyone\Nelse observing her today, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.53,0:06:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Who hired you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.24,0:06:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.58,0:06:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That tube was lying on the floor,\Nso I was just throwing it away...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.29,0:07:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Well, why don't we have the\Npalace guard listen to the rest of your story?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.46,0:07:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Obi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.96,0:07:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, please excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.10,0:07:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a strange way to gather companions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.60,0:07:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's taken a long time, but well,\Nyou are the ones who will have a hard time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.77,0:07:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.20,0:07:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.45,0:07:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,More okay than you, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.79,0:07:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.45,0:07:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You heard from the master, right?\NThat people would come investigate you in swarms?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.00,0:07:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like they'll gain\Nanything from doing that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.00,0:07:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm sure there are folks\Nwho can't give up that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.35,0:08:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss, can I ask what you think of\Nwhat the master is doing as a prince?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.06,0:08:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I think... it's very much like Zen...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.15,0:08:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? And that's good enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.48,0:08:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.74,0:08:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,He acted proud even when we had just met--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.74,0:08:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,He loves his country--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.57,0:08:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,He has Kiki and Mitsuhide--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.45,0:08:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen's always been a prince, and there\Nare people who act because of that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.91,0:08:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,When I gave you permission\Nto leave the grounds by yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.04,0:08:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I did think of the possibility\Nthat you wouldn't come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.09,0:08:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.22,0:08:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not just Miss Kiki and Mitsuhide.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.09,0:08:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you being here is also\Na part of who he is as a prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.18,0:08:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That prince... What good\Nwould come of me defeating him?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.98,0:08:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.36,0:08:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't laugh at that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.19,0:08:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.61,0:09:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Of all things, I just keep hearing about\Nhow Zen is made fun of because I'm with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.74,0:09:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm adding to his worries--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.08,0:09:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.87,0:09:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you so angry about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.21,0:09:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,E-Even though I've already\Ndecided where I want to be,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.75,0:09:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm mad at myself for not\Nknowing how to get here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.09,0:09:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Like with the punishment for Laxdo...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.09,0:09:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, Zen, why don't we remove\NLaxdo from your jurisdiction for six months?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.31,0:09:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it's been bothering me,\Nwhat good would come of me going there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.89,0:09:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, so you were trying to go to Fort Laxdo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.94,0:09:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you were talking about\Njackets and medicine and a horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.90,0:09:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Z-Zen only said that everything's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.99,0:09:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though he was\Nmaking a fist as he said it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.50,0:09:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Trying to act cool...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.42,0:09:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We're back to talking about the master...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.25,0:09:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem to be regularly equipped\Nwith trying to act cool, too, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.67,0:10:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't how to act,\Nwhy don't you go looking for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.64,0:10:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Rather than languishing by the window,\Nyou're the type to take action, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.77,0:10:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know about going at it alone\Nlike you were trying to just now, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.19,0:10:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, there {\i1}was{\i0} a suspicious person around.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.61,0:10:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... you're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.11,0:10:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Like the master, she's the type to rush\Nin on her own if no one's around to stop her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.62,0:10:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,She probably doesn't realize\Nthat when she's by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.75,0:10:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If you really want to go,\NI'll take you to Laxdo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.63,0:10:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But I already went and came back, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.13,0:10:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.13,0:10:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The master and the others\Nseemed concerned about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.38,0:10:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and the people at the fort did\Ntake care of me while I was there,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.76,0:10:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,so I stopped by to see how they were doing\Nwhen I got permission to leave the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.77,0:10:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.82,0:11:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the sekko plant,\Nwhich only grows under snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.11,0:11:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like a rare herb.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.32,0:11:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That lil' guy, Shuka, was it?\NHe's the one who picked it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.12,0:11:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Shuka did...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.00,0:11:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is a report of the\Nprogress of everyone's condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.13,0:11:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, it's so detailed...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.34,0:11:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it look like it'll help?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.93,0:11:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm sure of it.\NIt'll connect to the next thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.69,0:11:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you got over here so easily...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.65,0:11:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, I'm not thinking\Nthat deeply about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.69,0:11:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true that you're\Nlike a wild animal, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.53,0:11:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Wild animal?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.82,0:11:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,They asked me to pass on some messages, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.53,0:11:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,There were so many that I forgot them, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.53,0:11:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But they all said,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.54,0:11:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,"We'll work hard!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.08,0:11:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.42,0:11:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.05,0:12:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to work hard, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.80,0:12:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Obi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.89,0:12:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.68,0:12:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, let's go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.02,0:12:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.89,0:12:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.19,0:12:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoops!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.07,0:12:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This again? Oh, dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.12,0:12:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Just watching you all is interesting...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.88,0:12:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just a spectator, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.51,0:12:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Up we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.05,0:12:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,People act because of him, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.76,0:12:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I picked a troublesome place to spectate...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.12,0:13:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I have returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.96,0:13:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiki, you're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.96,0:13:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen, look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.80,0:13:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.76,0:13:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,When I went to see how\Nthey were doing, I found this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.85,0:13:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.60,0:13:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, also, Kiki, did that get made?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.06,0:13:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait, Zen!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.36,0:13:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He's going to find Shirayuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.15,0:13:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirayuki? Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.82,0:13:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What did that note say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.36,0:13:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That note was from Obi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.99,0:13:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, Shirayuki was drunk\Nand couldn't come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.91,0:13:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's why he was in such a hurry...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.96,0:14:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirayuki was drunk? Is she all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.50,0:14:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Obi was with her, and Zen's going,\Ntoo, so I'm sure it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.05,0:14:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.60,0:14:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad she came to join us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.54,0:14:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a month since I've been outside, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.00,0:14:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir. I thought I'd give this to\Nyou once your house arrest was over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.59,0:14:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It came from that boy's arrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.14,0:15:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Because... he doesn't have a grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.48,0:15:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Atri...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.83,0:15:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, I thought there\Nwas something off about Atri...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.58,0:15:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I did, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.76,0:15:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to believe...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.84,0:15:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to try and believe...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.77,0:15:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Zen, you are a prince of this kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.15,0:15:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,There will definitely be someone you\Ncan trust among the people you meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.45,0:16:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If you prioritize your suspicions,\Nno one would be able to follow you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.33,0:16:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You should learn who your allies are first,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.13,0:16:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,before being caught up\Ntrying to find your enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.80,0:16:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not think you need to rush anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.76,0:16:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,As a prince of Clarines,\Nyou should learn what is important,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.81,0:16:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,one by one, without cutting any corners.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.81,0:16:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I am still inexperienced,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.31,0:16:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,but I will stay by your side\Nand become a man you can rely on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.37,0:16:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Please allow me to protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.90,0:17:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitsuhide!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.86,0:17:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He used my name...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.15,0:17:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I will become one, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.78,0:17:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Become what, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.69,0:17:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I will become a master\Nhis attendants can be proud of.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.12,0:17:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I'd like to say, anyway. But first--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.58,0:17:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll become stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.25,0:17:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Prince Zen!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.72,0:17:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Zen, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.22,0:17:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with that gross laugh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.77,0:17:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Gross?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.27,0:17:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I was just remembering how Zen said\NI was being too stiff when I called him Prince Zen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.48,0:17:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, I remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.70,0:18:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, what was the other\Nthing you gave Zen? Not the note.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.70,0:18:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen told me to get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.16,0:18:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That was...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.75,0:18:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.30,0:18:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You little--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.05,0:18:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you'd be in the medical wing...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.26,0:18:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't wander around!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.76,0:18:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I was looking for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.52,0:18:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.81,0:18:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. It looks like she still\Nhas alcohol in her system.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.77,0:18:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard from the palace guards\Nthat you caught someone suspicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.36,0:18:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. He appeared to be investigating Shirayuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.99,0:18:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just as you and the others said, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.41,0:18:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirayuki said she felt like\Nshe was being watched recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.66,0:18:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,A little while ago, she would have tried\Nto do something about it herself, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.55,0:19:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirayuki was trying to go to Laxdo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.34,0:19:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a little far, though,\Nso it ended with a walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.31,0:19:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. I made her worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.77,0:19:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you just go back together?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.48,0:19:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're busy, six months will fly by.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.82,0:19:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I had no choice but to go\Noutside and give her a piggyback ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.28,0:19:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't say anything, did I?\NWhy are you telling me already?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.49,0:19:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You looked like you were going to snap at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.70,0:19:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I was not!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.25,0:19:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But even though I said she could send you away,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.17,0:19:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,in the end, she didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.54,0:19:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Obi--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.01,0:19:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.68,0:19:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, well, I had a close call, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.35,0:19:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You did?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.93,0:19:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you were up against Shirayuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.31,0:19:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If she had reason to, she would\Nsend even {\i1}me{\i0} away, I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.57,0:20:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad this won't go to waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.78,0:20:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.45,0:20:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,My identification?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.20,0:20:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It was just issued.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.54,0:20:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Messenger for Clarines'\NSecond Prince. That's your title.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.25,0:20:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that all right? To give me\Nsomething like this so easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.05,0:20:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.59,0:20:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the result of learning what was\Nimportant, one by one, as a prince of Clarines.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.89,0:20:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.98,0:20:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because I believe...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.94,0:20:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,...in my own judgment,\Nthe judgment of my friends, and in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.57,0:20:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Master, your eyes are a beautiful color...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.20,0:20:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop messing around!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.74,0:20:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you make me your messenger\Nrather than Shirayuki's guard?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.67,0:20:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the important part.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.92,0:21:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, that won't be your only job, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.13,0:21:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, it's a restraint.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.30,0:21:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I'll be by Shirayuki, if anything\Nhappens to Shirayuki, you'll find out about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.47,0:21:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,There aren't many who would\Nstick their noses in knowing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.77,0:21:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.27,0:21:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I will become better at\Nprotecting what's important to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.79,0:21:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen's not coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.33,0:21:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He's probably talking to Obi, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.96,0:21:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The stars are close tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.55,0:21:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Haven't they always been like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.51,0:21:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.27,0:21:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like getting some exercise.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.48,0:21:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll keep you company.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.81,0:22:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Time flows on, and days turn into months...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.81,0:22:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,In this changing world,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.61,0:22:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,there are things that do not change or waver.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.83,0:22:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,To have many people\NI trust constantly by my side...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.92,0:22:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That is something I will always hope for...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.21,0:22:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,On this path that I chose\Nand continue forward on...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.94,0:24:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Those with high rank won't\Nlisten to those with no rank.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.57,0:24:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a beautiful bird.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.40,0:24:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,How will you protect what you want to protect?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.41,0:24:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I will do all I can to make sure\Nthat doesn't happen to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.54,0:24:20.08,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,"Episode 10: Inexperienced Heart, Going Deeper"
